Sarah Imovbioh ( ka amụrụ n'ụbọchị nke 24 n'ọnwa Mee n'afọ 1992) bụ onye egwuregwu basketball nke PEAC-Pécs na ndị otu mba Naịjirịa.
O sonyere na 2018 FIBA Women's Basketball World Cup
O sonyekwara na 2019 2019 Women's Afrobasket ebe o meriri ọla edo na ndị otu egwuregwu basketball ụmụ nwanyị Naịjirịa.
